{"tid":43351,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［男］去旅行有無雪靴好推薦","createTime":"2016-12-17T12:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T20:46:43.000Z","uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e89549e54553bc1e9ebb433556ef21e362f061","tid":43351,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"過一個禮拜會去好凍嘅地方旅行<br />\n有無咩行得山防滑又保暖嘅靴or鞋推介<br />\n預左喺香港好少會著所以唔想太貴 budget唔過一千有無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跪求牌子或地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bea624f78216e152bed998388ff3d23eb421fc","tid":43351,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a6ff9e1227611e2ceb56b9918e138b2192f6df","tid":43351,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"61ea2e6a9f0b42ee41a4e823364790a004bb6883","tid":43351,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"唔過一千？！行得山防滑又保暖嘅靴？就呢對啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130427/large/27la5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130427%2Flarge%2F27la5p3.jpg&h=1481de02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b81ec75e341e64df4544ff990df308faf95b9264","tid":43351,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"7年前我買對mammut折左都2字頭，而家你想唔過千？<br />\n防滑：溶過雪既地抓得實唔會冼到仆街<br />\n保暖：對鞋唔掂，上身着幾多件都無用，啲寒氣係對腳到漏上黎<br />\n安全：冼到仆街頂多比人笑，靚鞋最緊要防r柴<br />\n你要平呀？good luck"},{"pid":"1801acb2fc8515b42a4c0a760f1a9c9eaa827108","tid":43351,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"唔記得左打<br />\n行山要求比行街高好多，防R方面由其是<br />\n如果你真係行山，唔係諗住call飛行服務隊，買對好啲既啦<br />\n上年大帽山有版你睇<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀書時期得閒會飛去玩下雪既回流巴"},{"pid":"c8340b96d59406fc0d93f3bdafbb39ca6002dd53","tid":43351,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔過一千？！行得山防滑又保暖嘅靴？就呢對啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130427/large/27la5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130427%2Flarge%2F27la5p3.jpg&h=1481de02&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細佬我未見大蛇痾屎唔知行情 唔好意思囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92afa981ea8701a737d77d13e3390afa3af7a16","tid":43351,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7年前我買對mammut折左都2字頭，而家你想唔過千？<br />\n防滑：溶過雪既地抓得實唔會冼到仆街<br />\n保暖：對鞋唔掂，上身着幾多件都無用，啲寒氣係對腳到漏上黎<br />\n安全：冼到仆街頂多比人笑，靚鞋最緊要防r柴<br />\n你要平呀？good luck</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無買過唔太知價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw唔該晒巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefbaa2ec7476c996572e8c97d681ffdf5f77ad0","tid":43351,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:38:12.000Z","msg":"認真行雪山既話 去當地租行山用品啦 例如雪抓？雪釘？ 唔知叫咩名 同埋拐杖 同埋要帶頭燈 如果去北歐 好早日落"},{"pid":"171dcd24cb892f9d584a52ef132df3a5cb1a2f2e","tid":43351,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:39:17.000Z","msg":"之前著過timberland黃靴加好厚既襪去<br />\n再加行雪山gear<br />\n搖粒絨襪先夠厚"},{"pid":"dd508f717